00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,839
Haven't heard from him since.

287
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:45,200
Su Yi went with him.

288
00:17:46,080 --> 00:17:47,160
Su Yi.

289
00:17:48,320 --> 00:17:49,920
He's back working at the bar.

290
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,240
Which one.

291
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,919
After the breakup.

292
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:02,280
We haven't been able to reach him.

293
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,040
Not sure.

294
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,439
I'm talking about Su Yi.

295
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:08,440
What's wrong with him.

296
00:18:08,887 --> 00:18:11,447
What's the name of Su Yi's bar.

297
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,720
Uh... Gimel... I think.

298
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,400
It's called Glimmer, right.

299
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:18,480
Glimmer.

300
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,680
Glimmer.

301
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:25,999
Hey.

302
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:28,000
Are you free after work later.

303
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:31,080
Still working.

304
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:32,160
Stop working.

305
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:33,160
Let's go get a drink.

306
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:34,720
Like this.

307
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:35,960
At Su Yi's place

308
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,120
I'll help you sound
out Su Bai's intentions.

309
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,040
Hmm.

310
00:18:54,041 --> 00:18:55,840
Do you have other bartenders here.

311
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:57,440
No, just me.

312
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:00,480
I remember this is
definitely the right bar.

313
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,960
Maybe he's not here today.

314
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,879
Since we're already here.

315
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,880
Let's have a drink.

316
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:16,880
Enjoy your drinks.

317
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,440
Here.

318
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,679
The reason they did that.

319
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:41,079
Is because we wrote the plot to that point.

320
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:42,199
They had no choice but to do it.

321
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,520
Right, they couldn't avoid it.

322
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,920
We wrote the script.

323
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,960
We could tone down the earlier parts.

324
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,359
Let them progress to.

325
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:49,080
Holding hands.

326
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,080
Kissing.

327
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:52,200
Weaken the plot progression.

328
00:19:52,560 --> 00:19:54,480
Make them keep at least one meter apart.

329
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:55,920
When they get intimate.

330
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:57,719
Have one person immediately
push the other away.

331
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:58,920
That's not love at all.

332
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,400
They're lovers.

333
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:13,400
Without passion between them.

334
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:16,560
Can they still be called lovers.

335
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,400
Listen.

336
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:32,439
Su Bai.

337
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,440
Is stubborn.

338
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:36,400
He blows small matters out of proportion.

339
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:40,240
He's both stubbornly
serious and oversensitive.

340
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,320
And completely inflexible.

341
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:46,879
I'm running around the film set.

342
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,200
Without a moment's rest.

343
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:50,000
Then I come home to manage his moods.

344
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,440
Is this easy for me.

345
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,440
It's really not.

346
00:20:56,560 --> 00:20:58,160
Every time he offends someone.

347
00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:00,440
I'm the one bowing and scraping.

348
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,960
Making apologies.

349
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:03,360
Right.

350
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:05,560
It's good to have artistic standards.

351
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,600
But you can't fight the system.

352
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:09,680
Hmm

353
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,040
I've advised him many times

354
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:12,279
I said.

355
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:14,839
You need to be nicer to the producers.

356
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:16,240
And investors.

357
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,280
More polite.

358
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:18,840
But he won't listen.

359
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,559
I mean.

360
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:24,200
How much pressure have I endured for him.

361
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:25,399
How many bullets have I taken for him.

362
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,640
He doesn't see any of it.

363
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:29,960
I'm becoming a human pincushion.

364
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,200
I'll fix the script.

365
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,560
Don't be angry anymore.

366
00:21:53,760 --> 00:21:54,680
Come on.

367
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:55,680
Let's.

368
00:21:55,681 --> 00:21:56,999
Take care of each other.

369
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,000
Okay.

370
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:00,680
As long as we're not lovers.

371
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:04,080
Everything will be fine.

372
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,999
Can we stop talking about this.

373
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,079
No.

374
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:13,400
Why avoid the subject again.

375
00:22:16,280 --> 00:22:17,280
I don't want to talk.

376
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:18,600
I can't explain.

377
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:22,040
Take our last production.

378
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:24,200
They wanted their own actors.

379
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,080
He stubbornly refused.

380
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:28,240
If I hadn't mediated.

381
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:30,360
That project would've collapsed.

382
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,640
And he criticized me.

383
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,160
Called me a social climber.

384
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,840
How could he.

385
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,400
Absolutely unreasonable.

386
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,759
Fine.

387
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,720
Don't want to talk.

388
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,439
Stay away from me.

389
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:49,680
Do whatever, I'm tired.

390
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,800
And now you're giving me attitude.

391
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,240
Just you wait.

392
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:01,000
Even if you beg me to get back together.

393
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,480
I wouldn't agree even if hell freezes over.

394
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,160
Su Bai.

395
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,840
You'll live to regret this.

396
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,679
Oh sir, good evening.

397
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,920
We're closing soon, I'm afraid.

398
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,600
I can feel...

399
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:36,920
there's something unfolding.

400
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:27,439
There was only one
customer in this heavy rain.

401
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:29,480
Seems like an actor too.

402
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,360
Who is it.

403
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:34,360
Take a guess.

404
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:35,680
Pei Jia
